# Welcome to my data analytics portfolio!  
This repository showcases a selection of projects demonstrating my ability to transform raw data into actionable insights through analysis, visualization, and business storytelling.  
These projects were completed as part of the **Data Analytics Career Accelerator** from **The London School of Economics and Political Science (LSE)** in collaboration with **FourthRev**, along with independent analytical work.

