## 🧠 Featured Projects

### [1️⃣ 2Market Data Analysis](./2Market-Data-Analysis)
![2Market Banner](./2Market-Data-Analysis/banner.png)

**Objective:**  
To help **2Market**, a retail company, design a data-driven marketing campaign by understanding its customers, products, and advertising channels.

**Key Highlights:**
- Cleaned and structured customer and sales data using Excel and PostgreSQL  
- Built interactive dashboards in Tableau showing demographic insights and sales patterns  
- Identified top-performing products and most effective advertising channels  
- Recommended targeted marketing strategies based on data trends  

**Tools:** Excel | SQL (PostgreSQL) | Tableau

---

### [2️⃣ NHS Capacity and Resource Utilisation Analysis](./NHS-Capacity-Analysis)
![NHS Banner](./NHS-Capacity-Analysis/banner.png)

**Objective:**  
To help the **National Health Service (NHS)** evaluate whether to expand its capacity by analysing resource utilisation across its networks.

**Key Highlights:**
- Conducted time-series and utilisation analysis on appointment and capacity datasets  
- Visualized performance by location, service setting, and healthcare provider type  
- Found underutilisation and recommended optimising existing resources instead of expanding capacity  
- Suggested areas for further analysis (e.g., post-2021 appointment decline)  

**Tools:** Python (Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn) | Jupyter Notebook  

---

### [3️⃣ Turtle Games Customer Trends Analysis](./Turtle-Games-Insights)
![Turtle Games Banner](./Turtle-Games-Insights/banner.png)

**Objective:**  
To help **Turtle Games** improve overall sales performance by identifying customer trends and loyalty drivers.

**Key Highlights:**
- Analyzed demographic variables (age, remuneration, spending score) vs. loyalty points  
- Found positive correlation between spending and loyalty accumulation  
- Segmented customers into five clusters based on income and spending behaviour  
- Performed sentiment analysis using TextBlob on customer summaries and reviews  
- Derived insights to improve loyalty programs and marketing strategies  

**Tools:** Python (Pandas, Seaborn, TextBlob) | NLP | Jupyter Notebook  

